{"tid":1276921,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我只係一個好普通嘅人，但我想盡一分力","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T05:27:00.000Z","uid":63129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9cf6c36c170a6650b712e5fa6cbc9530f60f59","tid":1276921,"uid":63129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"願今次抗爭終可得勝，願暴君不得善終，義士長存！<br />\n<br />\n他們先是<span style=\"color: red;\">無視</span>你，再來是<span style=\"color: red;\">嘲笑</span>你，接著他們與你戰斗，最后<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你贏了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n願天國嘅三位義士保佑香港，與我們同存！<br />\n<br />\n就是因為<span style=\"color: red;\">自己非常怕死</span>，所以才會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">對別人的死亡流下眼淚</span></span><br />\n<br />\n願世界及更多人明白義士嘅苦衷，站在抗爭者的一方，讓暴政崩潰，讓香港得以自由及和平！<br />\n<br />\n要活就要像明天你就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">會死去一般活著</span></span>。要學習就要好像你會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">永遠活著一般學習</span></span>"}]}